## Milestone 4 — First Battle Loop (Normal Camp) (Week 3) ✅

**Goal:** Implement a basic auto-combat loop vs. a small enemy pack, using engine pipeline.

### Tasks
- [x] Implement `phaser/PhaserGame.tsx` wrapper to mount Phaser inside React.
