- [x] Implement `phaser/scenes/BattleScene.ts`:
  - [x] Draw player sprite and 2–3 enemy sprites.
  - [x] Handle a simple tick loop (e.g. every 500ms) where:
    - [x] Player auto-attacks nearest enemy using `resolveDamage()`.
    - [x] Enemies auto-attack player at their own attackSpeed.
  - [x] On enemy death, emit `ENEMY_DIED` event with drop results from `dropResolver`.
  - [x] On player death, emit `PLAYER_DIED` event.
- [x] Implement `phaser/events/PhaserEventBus.ts` (simple EventEmitter bridge).
