- [x] Implement `screens/BattleScreen.tsx` using UI spec:
  - [x] Player HUD (HP, resource, barrier).
  - [x] Embed `<PhaserGame />` canvas.
  - [x] Enemy HUD (HP bars for current enemies).
  - [x] Combat log (last 5 lines).
