- [x] On [Fight (Auto)] from World Map, navigate to `/battle` with selected node.

### Exit criteria
- [x] You can click Market Camp → Fight → see player auto-attacking until all enemies die or player dies.
- [x] Combat log shows damage numbers from the real damage pipeline, not hard-coded.
